node.text: Ya boy has finally arrived to @roblox. 4pm PDT 13th August / 12am BST 14th August, I’ll be performing songs from my album All Over The Place as well as celebrating with the Roblox community. There’s currently a launch party Experience happening right now with exclusive merch and more in Roblox, so go and enjoy and I’ll see you all soon
